# Public URL of the deployed Cloudflare Worker AI proxy (see /worker) - not
# secret, just an endpoint. The real OpenRouter key lives ONLY as that
# Worker's OPENROUTER_API_KEY secret (`npx wrangler secret put OPENROUTER_API_KEY`
# inside /worker), never in this file or any VITE_ variable.
VITE_AI_PROXY_URL=
